install arduino
1-in arduino ide:
go to "file->preferences->additional bord manager urls" and add this line
https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json

2-go to :"tools->board->board manager"
install "esp32 by espressif system"

tools menu settings:
board:doit esp 32 devkit v1
baude rate :921600
flash frequency:80Mhz
programmer:avrisp mkII


to program board hold boot key during connection

